flowchart TD
    A[Admin/Staff opens shared/applications.php or shared/verify-qr.php] --> B[Search/filter applicant]
    B --> C[Open application details]
    C --> D[Review profile, requirements, notes, QR history]
    D --> E{Need status update?}
    E -->|No| F[Keep current status]
    E -->|Yes| G[Apply allowed transition]

    G --> H{Current status}
    H -->|draft| H1[under_review]
    H -->|under_review| H2[for_interview or rejected]
    H -->|needs_resubmission| H3[under_review or rejected]
    H -->|for_interview| H4[interview_passed or rejected]
    H -->|interview_passed| H5[for_soa]
    H -->|for_soa| H6[soa_received]
    H -->|soa_received| H7[awaiting_payout or disbursed]
    H -->|awaiting_payout| H8[disbursed]
    H -->|disbursed/rejected| H9[End state]

    H1 --> I[Update applications.status]
    H2 --> I
    H3 --> I
    H4 --> I
    H5 --> I
    H6 --> I
    H7 --> I
    H8 --> I
    H9 --> I

    I --> J[Save review notes and optional SOA deadline]
    J --> K[Insert audit_logs]
    K --> L[Create notifications for applicant]
    L --> M[Optional SMS status update via template]

    M --> N{Status is disbursed?}
    N -->|No| O[Finish]
    N -->|Yes| P[Create/confirm disbursement record]
    P --> O
